    • Constructor Detail

      • CountingTutorial

        public CountingTutorial()
        Creates a specific counting game designed to teach the user how to play. In addition to everything a Counting Game keeps track of, a CountingTutorial keeps track of what tip it is currently on, how long the tip has been displayed and whether the tip is visible or not
